{"tid":1366914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［有感］象徵自由","createTime":"2019-07-26T06:01:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T06:33:26.000Z","uid":287471,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"510c4736d0154f98da9ef7592ce3ed071eb50003","tid":1366914,"uid":287471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UqkFPSm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUqkFPSm.png&h=32f1e90c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95pZ5qH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95pZ5qH.png&h=1ad41ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZXwWxo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZXwWxo.png&h=cd6bb891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呢個面具係出自netflix 一套西班牙劇 <br />\n就係講緊一班互不相識的罪犯打劫造幣廠<br />\n每一次見大眾都會戴住呢個面具<br />\n初頭大眾好憎呢班罪犯<br />\n但係政府背後的政治手段越揭越黑<br />\n人民開始支持罪犯呢啲反政府的示威<br />\n而面具象徴緊自由的權利<br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐，我係想講我地而家有好多撐警既人，都加入左我地既陣營，我地已經有人民的支持。我地本來都互不相識，但係我地都有同一個夢，一個屬於香港人的夢！而家我地要做就係一齊企出來，著黑色3。而吾係凈係坐係屋企，話咩驚比人打。<br />\n就算比人打！聽日我地都要一齊比人打！一齊反擊！<br />\n男既著裝！女既後援！</span><br />\n7.27 元朗見</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oS2pxe6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoS2pxe6.png&h=f0d27db3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"14e596284cfcb341172c56a2cc55f6286d3e5dcb","tid":1366914,"uid":287471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:02:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba591c770f515677ce15d3b3cc26ac765a22d00c","tid":1366914,"uid":287471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2786186202edc52ba4aae70188300a7bb5b7346","tid":1366914,"uid":287471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:03:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f3abf488b2fa8027b4a1086bf122eb36e9667b","tid":1366914,"uid":14936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"有追開 好撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但幾時出第四季"},{"pid":"92c2a0c78cfea2497d7ab2bb5d5516953828c76c","tid":1366914,"uid":287471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94f3abf488b2fa8027b4a1086bf122eb36e9667b","tid":1366914,"uid":14936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"有追開 好撚好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但幾時出第四季"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T06:33:26.000Z","msg":"佢出左第三季 我一日追哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}